{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And if we say that password, we will receive a package and then bring it back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The other two that went with me was supposed to remain there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "However, we wound up in Kecskemet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then we took an-- if I'm not mistaken-- a narrow-gauge railroad to a town by the name Gyula.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And from there, you can see already the mountains start.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that's where the Hungarian-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] previously, you know, the Hungarian-Transylvanian border was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we, we were instructed to go-- a certain farmer-- a, a Hungarian farmer would meet us at a certain place, who was from the other side of the border, and will take us across the mountain.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And after we left just the first upgrade, we were walking, and we ran into a German patrol.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they caught us and took us in, and, and started beating us with the leg of a chair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I kept on saying, hey, I am this and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They, they never took my pants down, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But they-- after about an hour, or an hour-and-a-half interrogation, they just let me go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, don't associate with Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know that you were together with Jewish people?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said to them, no, come on, now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know whatever happened to the two other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wound up in-- across the border because of-- the, the, the, the Hungarian peasant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let him go immediately, because he said, I have nothing to do with these people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just met them here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I'm a farmer from here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't even take him in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just took us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, I, I met up with him and crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
